# Research & Automation

- **Documentation**: Use `context7` by default for any npm package versioning questions.
- **n8n Integration**: When asked to "automate X," use the `mcp-n8n` server to list existing workflows or suggest a new trigger-action node structure.
- **Up-to-Date Info**: Use `brave-search` for any errors involving "deprecated" features or recent library releases.